    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## Define the data path and discover HTML files\n",
        "\n",
        "Use either:\n",
        "\n",
        "- `../data/SEC-10K-2024-HTML`\n",
        "- a mounted Google Drive folder containing the SEC HTML corpus"
